import React from 'react'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; import getEstimation from '../util/PanelCalculator' import { Table, TableBody, TableRow, TableCell, Typography, Box, Paper } from '@mui/material'; const EstimationDetailsPanel = () => { const battery = useSelector((state: any) => state.battery); const noofbatteries = battery.noOfBatteries; const estimation = getEstimation(battery, noofbatteries); return ( <> {"Estimation Details"} {"Land Required for Site:- "} {estimation.landHeight + "FT(width) X " + estimation.landWidth + "FT(height)"} {"Site Energy:- "} {estimation.siteEnergy + " MWh"} {"Cost:- "} {"$" + estimation.price} {"No of Transformers Required:- "} {estimation.noOfTransformers}
); } export default EstimationDetailsPanel;
